data.description: Welcome to your own private paradise! This stunning lake house offers the perfect retreat. Nestled on a private lake, you'll enjoy views of sparkling waters and captivating sunsets. Step in and be greeted by a screened-in pool and hot tub, providing the ultimate relaxation experience. The spacious Florida room, complete with heat and air conditioning, allows you to embrace the beautiful outdoors while maintaining year-round comfort. Inside, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home showcases a large living room and a family room with a cozy fireplace, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The entire home boasts brand new flooring, adding a modern touch to the already inviting ambiance. Privacy is ensured with the addition of brand-new privacy fencing, allowing you to fully unwind in your own sanctuary. The bathrooms have been recently upgraded, providing a luxurious feel to your everyday routine. Enjoy the breathtaking lakeside views from the deck that runs along the lakeshore, while the covered lanai offers the perfect spot for outdoor dining and entertainment. Additional features include an irrigation system that cleverly utilizes lake water instead of City water, reducing costs and environmental impact. Don't miss your chance to own this impeccable lake house that offers an idyllic blend of both relaxation and elegance.
